body:
@laanwj good point! I actually don't have much hands-on experience with Tor inbounds.
I can't verify what you say atm, but yeah, *if* they look like 127.0.0.1, they will be grouped with "comes from localhost" until #8973.

I think it's fine to merge it as-is, and then when #8973 comes the grouping can be improved.

